    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, functional choice for a buyer looking for reliability without the premium price of a newer model. While the engine and transmission are dependable, the exterior shows its history with some visible scratches, minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small door dings. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays typical wear on the driver's seat and some aged plastic trim. It has been recently serviced, though it will eventually need new tires and a look at a slow window motor. This is a practical, honest car for someone who values utility and steady performance over a flawless appearance.",
      "price": 18500.0,
